Dialogs.Dialog: Hehe, you wanna be a spoiled child？
What？ You're acting like a kid.
Hehe, what do you want to do？
Can we stay like this a little longer？
Sorry. Can we stay like this...？
I think this is good. Yeah.
Sorry, can we not do this？
This is not acceptable, I think.
Sorry, this is totally not good...
Hehe, do you think I'll be happy？
Sorry, this is a little... You know...？
Was that supposed to be funny？
Hm, for this, I have to refuse.
Um, what is it all of a sudden？
Hehe, I'm in a good mood.
Ah, no. Don't look at me.
What？ You want to be spoiled？
You wanna act more like lovers？
You want to come closer to me, huh？
Isn't it too soon for this？
Hey, I'm not going to spoil you.
Sorry, I'm not in the mood for that.
Hmm, you want to do this...
It's quite big... I mean your hand...
Okay, okay. You don't have to grab my hand that tightly.
Fine, in return, you'll have to grab my hand tightly.
You can keep holding my hand forever.
Ah, sorry. This is just... You know？
Hmm... Can we not do this？
Do you understand？ If so, let go of me.
It's warm. Even warmer than my body temperature, I think.
If we don't be careful, we might get sunburn.
Urgh. The weather is too hot for us to walk close to each other.
It's hot, but I don't mind getting more heat from your warm body.
I want to eat something cold now.
In such hot weather, it's good to be a boy, right？
Although I'm sweating, this feels good.
It's a chance for me to lose some weight in such hot weather, I think.
Somehow... My hands have become numb.
It feels good to hold hands in such cold weather, right？
I want to get under my blanket.
I don't mind if you hold my hand.
Wanna come closer？ Come on here...
My hands become cold. Will you hold them？
Wanna make me feel warm？ Hehe...
Somehow, I'm scared... I'm getting nervous.
No, it's too dangerous to move.
This is okay. We are together, all right？
I'm a bit scared... But we will stay together, right？
I'm not scared. I'm not scared...
Sorry. I'm not happy with that.
If we swing arms while walking, will we feel better？
If you get any closer, it will be difficult for us to walk.
We should get closer to each other, right？
Stop doing this, okay？ It's embarrassing.
Ah, are you getting embarrassed？ Hey, hey.
Hey, do you want me to stay closer to you？
Hey？ Do you want to hold onto my arm？
The weather is too hot for us to get closer.
Do you feel better now？ So I guess it's enough.
Um... Is this enough？ Not yet？
What？ You don't want to get lost, huh？
Okay, okay. This big sister will lead your way.
If you grab me firmly like this...
Huh？ Do your hands feel lonely？
Hehe, I wonder if you feel lonely.
Okay, I won't let go of your hand.
...Hmm, I think this is fine, but...
Hmm, sorry. Maybe we'll do this next time.
Hello？ What are you staring down there？
Don't keep staring at my lower body parts.
Do you feel motivated or something？
Why do you keep staring there？
I wonder if you only have one thing on your mind.
Ah, you might smell the insect repellant.
Are you okay？ Doesn't this make it difficult to walk？
This feels quite good, I think.
Doesn't that bother you？ Is it okay？
I kind of like it like this...
I wonder how others would see us as.
I feel like you monopolize me somehow.
Teeheehee. You hold my hand tightly.
Hmm... Will it be bad if we don't hold hands？
Let's hold this for later, okay？
Hmm...？ You really hold my hand tightly.
Doing this is not bad, I guess.
Eh？ You hand is sweaty. Hehe.
Um, fine. Just don't let go of my hand...
You can grab my hand tighter than that.
Hmm... This is too soon, okay？
This is a little too embarrassing, I think.
Ah, don't look at me like that.
Hehe, this is a little embarrassing, you know？
Hmm... Does this suit your tastes？
Don't keep staring at my legs.
If you keep looking at my lower body part, you'll become a hunchback.
When can I see you next time...？
Hehe. I'm fine. I don't feel lonely.
It's okay. We'll meet again, okay？
You don't want to leave？ Hehe, we'll meet again.
Um... I still don't want to leave...
Maybe we can do this later, okay？
Eh？ You don't want to leave, huh？
If you keep holding my arm, I can't go home.
Ah, maybe we should wait until later.
Hehe, maybe we'll do this next time, okay？
Um, let's have a good time together again.
Does this mean that you don't want to go home？
You like to touch my hair, huh？ Hehe.
Why are you touching my forehead？ It's okay though.
Why are you touching my forehead？ It's okay though.
My arm？ What is it？ Hmm, you like it？
It feels nice when our hands touch...
I like it when you touch my hair...
When you touch my forehead, I can feel a stream of happiness running through my whole body...
It's fine to walk arm in arm, but we must stay like this forever！ Just kidding.
This is only for you. I won't let anyone else touch my hair.
No, when you touch my ear, I feel overly sensitive...
....Hey, can I keep holding you like this forever？
Hey, touching a girl's hair is something very special, you know？
My ears are getting hot... If I get a fever, it must be your fault.
When you grab my hand, you grab my heart as well. Never let go, okay...？
Eh？ My forehead... This is embarrassing, but I don't hate it at all.
What？ Do you feel good when you touch my ears？
Can you hold my hand tightly？ I want to keep feeling your touch even when I've arrived home.
Hey, is my forehead very warm？ It's because of you, not because I have a fever.
No... When you grab my arm like that... I just can't resist...
I wish you would never let go of my hand and would stay with me like this forever.
